description: This file defines the API functions for managing XDSL parameters within the RDKXdslManager module, including getters and setters for various parameter types, as well as commit operations.

methods.name: XdslManagerGetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Retrieves a ULONG parameter value for the XDSL Manager.

methods.name: XdslManagerSetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Sets a ULONG parameter value for the XDSL Manager.

methods.name: XdslManagerCommit
methods.description: Commits the current configuration changes in the XDSL Manager.

methods.name: XdslManagerSetParamStringValue
methods.description: Sets a string parameter value for the XDSL Manager.

methods.name: XdslManagerGetParamStringValue
methods.description: Retrieves a string parameter value for the XDSL Manager.

methods.name: XdslManagerGetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Retrieves a boolean parameter value for the XDSL Manager.

methods.name: XdslManagerSetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Sets a boolean parameter value for the XDSL Manager.
